FileContext - Class in fr.umlv.chathack.contexts
 
FileContext(int, String, FileOutputStream) - Constructor for class fr.umlv.chathack.contexts.FileContext
Constructor of a fileContext.
It contains informations about a file for download such as the file name, its size and its content in bytes.
The full content is not stored in this object, a buffer is filled up as data is received from the channel.

Frame - Interface in fr.umlv.chathack.resources.frames
 
frameComparator() - Method in class fr.umlv.chathack.contexts.Context
Makes and returns a frame comparator which compare 2 types of frame :
Download Frame and not Download Frame.
This comparator make the Download Frames less important than others frames, in order to send faster messages.
To conserve order in 2 Download Frames, the one which has been created first will be sent first.
